articles.author: Erika Tulfo
articles.title: CVS names new CEO in the wake of layoffs and poor stock performance - CNN
articles.description: America’s largest drug store chain named a new chief executive officer on Friday, with longtime CVS Health executive David Joyner replacing Karen Lynch.
